    "We do this stage of experimentation with the 112 equal length problems in the 2019 version of the UCR archive (Dau et al. 2019).",
    "Performance on these datasets, or some subset thereof, has been used to support every proposed approach, so this allows us to make a fair comparison of algorithms.",
